Rating: 4
My husband and I made this last night and were REALLY impressed with how it came out. The flavor of the spices was wonderful and the contrast of the Moroccan spices with the beautiful orange honey sauce was just perfect. We made a few alterations - such as brining the hens for 36 hours before cooking them (which made them super juicy) and we did them on the rotisserie of our grill as opposed to in the oven but the flavors really were fantastic! Thanks so much for the recipe!

Rating: 4
This spice rub was terrific and delicately permeated the carrots which made them unusually tasty. Didn't bother with the honey orange sauce, will try that next time. Great recipe for a unique,delicious, new way to make game hens! B.J. Harrick

