Rating: 4
This recipe is SO easy and SO tasty. I have made it 3 times now and my husband has raved about it every time. I tossed the carrots (pre- peeled baby carrots for me, save even more time) with olive oil, salt and pepper before roasting; they caramelize and are a perfect accompaniament. Tried the orange- honey sauce for the first time tonight; it is terrific but not essential for the recipe. Recipe also halves easily for two. This is my "go-to" Cornish game hen recipe!

