I've used Epicurious for years and never felt compelled to write a review until now. Living near top San Fran restaurant Gary Danko (author of this recipe) I had to try this, being a regular game hen griller and baker (beats chicken all of the time, right?. This is truly one of the best new recipes I've gathered in years. Substituted Madeira for the wine as it was all I had in the house. Everyone raved about this, even my semi-slightly sophisticated 6 and 8 year olds. Have already forwarded it to two of my expert chef friends.

