Rating: 3
The hens were delicious, but I cooked them an hour rather than 40 minutes because they didn't seem done, and all of the liquid cooked away. I deglazed the pan with some wine instead. I might try cooking it at 350 for 1 hour next time. Also, I only used 10 figs, and this was more than enough for two people. Since the olives I used were small, I would use more next time.

